orkstation (it can also be faster, depending on the workstation...).\nAnother is that sessions ‚Äúexpire‚Äù after a period of inactivity, freeing computing resources for other users.\nThe session can easily be restarted, however, with the click of a button.\nIn some contexts, ","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"hqg9Uc74cY"},{"type":"link","url":"https://mybinder.org/","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Binder","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"zbpiMb5QWe"}],"urlSource":"https://mybinder.org/","key":"i17pFjHOMO"},{"type":"text","value":" implementations also have constraints on reading and writing data files.","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"EEASBWVxg0"}],"key":"qyafY9pahK"}],"key":"UguWVjOhLS"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Executable models running locally on your computer","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"duwebHSvnH"}],"key":"PJxtbLB9Q3"},{"type":"text","value":" can be launched from downloaded copies of the source repositories, or from copies of those repositories already in the source materials for this book.\nExecutable Jupyter notebooks containing models (and supporting Python libraries, if needed) are also incorporated into the book as ","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"BNU9TboobO"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"subrepos","position":{"start":{"line":